Package: MSM
Type: Package
Title: Forecasting Volatility With Markov Switching Multifractal Model
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2017-03-25
Author: Waleem Alausa
Maintainer: Waleem Alausa <alausa.babs@gmail.com>
Description: It fits Markov Switching Multifractal Volatility model
    to log returns, and provides volatility forecast based on the
    fitted model. It can also be used to decompose returns into multiple
    volatility components/ volatility clusters.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1),
    Rsolnp,
    truncnorm,
    reshape2,
    ggplot2,
    plyr,
    gtable,
    scales,
    munsell,
    colorspace
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.7),
    stats
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
LazyLoad: yes
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
